                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-medium text-white mb-1">LinkedIn</h4>
                                <p class="text-white/60 text-sm mb-2">Professional networking and quick messages</p>
                                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/carlospolanco" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">
